{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/til/technical-writing/one/07-lists-and-tables-2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bestalign's dev blog","categories":[{"displayText":"홈","priority":0,"name":"home","url":"/"},{"displayText":"TIL","priority":1,"name":"til","url":"/til"},{"displayText":"개발","priority":2,"name":"dev","url":"/dev"},{"displayText":"독서","priority":3,"name":"reading","url":"/reading"},{"displayText":"번역","priority":4,"name":"translation","url":"/translation"},{"displayText":"일기","priority":5,"name":"everydaylife","url":"/everydaylife"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c1ef68ac-fea7-574a-8315-1da393387e16","excerpt":"…","html":"<h4 id=\"적절한-테이블을-추가하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%A0%88%ED%95%9C-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EC%9D%84-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"적절한 테이블을 추가하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적절한 테이블을 추가하라</h4>\n<p>테이블을 만들때는 다음을 고려하라:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>각 컬럼에 적절한 헤더를 추가하라.</li>\n<li>한 셀에 너무 많은 텍스트를 넣지마라. 텍스트가 두 문장 이상이라면 더 좋은 형식이 있는지 생각하라.</li>\n<li>한 컬럼의 셀들은 같은 형식으로 맞춰라.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"리스트와-테이블을-소개하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EC%99%80-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EC%9D%84-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"리스트와 테이블을 소개하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리스트와 테이블을 소개하라</h4>\n<p>리스트와 테이블이 무엇에 관한 적인지 소개하라. 소개 문장의 끝은 콜론(:)으로 마무리하라.</p>\n<h5 id=\"example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#example\" aria-label=\"example permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example</h5>\n<p>The following table contains a few key facts about some popular programming langauges:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Languages</th>\n<th>Inventor</th>\n<th>Year Introduced</th>\n<th>Key Feature</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Lisp</td>\n<td>John McCarthy</td>\n<td>1958</td>\n<td>recursion</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>C++</td>\n<td>Bjarne Stroustrup</td>\n<td>1979</td>\n<td>OOP</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Python</td>\n<td>Guido Van Rossum</td>\n<td>1994</td>\n<td>simplicity</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/tech-writing/one/lists-and-tables\">Google Dev Technical Writing 1 - Lists and Tables</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Lists and Tables 2","category":"til","date":"July 03, 2021","updated":null,"description":null,"tags":["technical writing"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/06-lists-and-tables-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Lists and Tables 1"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/08-paragraphs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Paragraphs"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c1ef68ac-fea7-574a-8315-1da393387e16","previousPostId":"fd4b67cd-7c98-5076-897b-abb75bc2816d","nextPostId":"272069c8-b4d1-5ad2-a06f-3d80d4cb0538"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}